## 1️⃣ Executive Summary

This report presents the findings of a comprehensive web application
penetration test conducted on DVWA (Damn Vulnerable Web Application)
and OWASP Juice Shop as part of Project 2 of the Zaalimaa Development
Pvt Ltd Internship Program.

The testing was conducted over 3 weeks following the OWASP Top 10:2025
framework. A total of **15 vulnerabilities** were identified and
successfully exploited, ranging from Critical to High severity.

### Key Findings:
- **7 Critical** vulnerabilities identified
- **8 High** vulnerabilities identified
- **15 Total** vulnerabilities confirmed
- **5 OWASP** categories covered
- **2 Platforms** tested (DVWA + Juice Shop)

